{"tid":892628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(My香港名單) 38名經濟學者聯署撐「明日大嶼」 填海才能成就香港","createTime":"2018-11-07T04:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T09:28:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"03006527bf0ca2c871d2a10cd8ba52e8495b0815","tid":892628,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1541549854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1541549854.jpg&h=0567558d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥於今年施政報告提出「明日大嶼願景」，本港38位經濟學者昨發表聯署聲明支持。這些專家認為，「明日大嶼願景」明顯是「上佳的選擇」，能為特區政府帶來可觀的財政收入。聲明更指，如今坊間認為填海興建人工島是「倒錢落海」或「燃燒儲備」，完全忽視土地是香港最寶貴的資產，特區政府可通過賣地回收增闢土地的成本。<br />\n<br />\n為此，包括團結香港基金顧問王于漸、雷鼎鳴、廖柏偉，嶺南大學校長鄭國漢、珠海學院商學院院長何濼生、前港區全國人大代表劉佩瓊等38位本港經濟學者發起和參與聯署聲明，力撐「願景」。<br />\n<br />\n　　聲明表示，「明日大嶼願景」推出以來，社會議論紛紛，有不少是立場先行及情緒化的口號，甚至流於煽動民情的民粹政治操作，所以不得不站出來，說明「明日大嶼願景」是可負擔的方案，更是上佳的投資。<br />\n<br />\n　　聲明分析指，「明日大嶼願景」財政收入肯定十分可觀。目前，特區政府初步估計「明日大嶼願景」總成本約5000億至6000億元（港幣，下同）。按特區政府最新資料，第一階段1000公頃的交椅洲填海，將提供4000萬平方呎商業樓面，按每呎樓面地價9000元的保守估計，商業土地收入約3600億元。<br />\n<br />\n此外，兩階段合共1700公頃填海，最多興建40萬個住宅單位，以公私營房屋比例70：30計算，即興建12萬個私人住宅及28萬個公營住宅。保守估計每個私人住宅土地收入約400萬元，12萬個私人住宅的土地收入約4800億元。因此，兩階段項目的賣地收入為8400億元。<br />\n<br />\n　　聲明表示，除了拍賣土地的收入及經濟收益外，還要計算多種社會效益，例如人工島將興建28萬夥公營房屋單位，還有康樂、運動、醫療等社區設施，社會效益不容忽視。<br />\n<br />\n　　聲明強調，香港土地價值不菲，從戰後到如今70多年，賣地收益一般遠超填海成本。如今坊間認為填海興建人工島是「倒錢落海」或者「燃燒儲備」，這是完全忽視土地是香港最寶貴的資產，特區政府可以通過賣地回收增闢土地的成本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1541561632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1541561632.jpg&h=f8236ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-11/07/content_1108118.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2018-11%2F07%2Fcontent_1108118.html&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43AEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=99abb67f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcd.com/content/2018-11/07/content_1108118.html</a>"},{"pid":"9a56b15408a2290bb39767552debe43bd3633119","tid":892628,"uid":53026,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"好呀，你38條友出錢無所謂"},{"pid":"49370738d8524cf0386a9a024fc76bd14801ff0d","tid":892628,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d808c905c64b469ce11b1407489233368d2015e3","tid":892628,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"整合賣港清算名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b862c1d849b242391f0eafd091bf3bb3dadf7337","tid":892628,"uid":154820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"好多支那名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f54932a36dfbbc522ce3885ac96ba1adcb6770","tid":892628,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"中大浸大港大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9a1e430bcec983301bb19e7b312a06c869000e","tid":892628,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"有幾多支那出世<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbada2591df63dbd168b8c1c432211785a071334","tid":892628,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"d專家食屎啦.jpg"},{"pid":"33726a1bccf00aacec52d6a553fa64ebe3763dfb","tid":892628,"uid":159350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"竟然冇我城"},{"pid":"c8b185fab20f973f3f126ba7d3cd08375dce1a17","tid":892628,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49370738d8524cf0386a9a024fc76bd14801ff0d","tid":892628,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"9a56b15408a2290bb39767552debe43bd3633119","tid":892628,"uid":53026,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"好呀，你38條友出錢無所謂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PjhS5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PjhS5b.png&h=e728e7aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a031017f1c59b99a5eea3d9cfe9fdf83947cf3d6","tid":892628,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"雷鼎鳴鄭國漢都簽<br />\n不如問下點解同窗阿梁兆輝點解唔簽"},{"pid":"5e4caf331f4cc6624f9d514c9eed33b6c60022d5","tid":892628,"uid":42751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"雷教授話佔中會破壞經濟，令香港唔見2500億，結果2014年GDP、HSI、樓價無跌過<br />\n專家食屎啦.jpg"},{"pid":"b672ff9a3e518bf380a0a63dde072aa891a8971e","tid":892628,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:48:00.000Z","msg":"38名經濟學者今日發表聯署支持方案，形容「明日大嶼」是上佳的投資，以政府財力應付計劃是綽綽有餘。綜合聯署内容，我們得出以下觀點：<br />\n<br />\n（1）香港土地寶貴，賣地必定可以收回填海成本，故此越填得多越賺得多，再多的土地都一樣會高價賣出，不存在過度供應的風險，經濟學上的供求曲綫不適用 (supply/demand curve)。<br />\n<br />\n（2）至於現成的荒置棕地農地，由於需要付出一定收回價，就由得它們繼續荒置，無所謂經濟學中的機會成本 (opportunity cost) 。<br />\n<br />\n（3) 人工島由於較接近市區中心，所需交通基建比在新界建設新市鎮為少。這裏假設新市鎮不能接駁或擴充現有集體運輸和道路網，而得出比興建全新跨海大橋更貴的結論，似乎沒有考慮經濟學中的規模經濟 (economy of scale)。<br />\n<br />\n經濟學有所謂「世上沒有免費午餐」，人工島不論對香港財政和環境生態都構成極大代價，不能單以增加土地供應就輕輕帶過。我們實在不明白，在目前政府完全沒有提供任何實質成本效益和回報分析的情況下，這些「經濟學家」爲何要急於表態支持興建人工島？就憑這些粗疏的論點，又怎能説服香港人興建人工島是上佳的投資選擇？到底是誰立場先行？<br />\n<br />\n思言財雋 Financier Conscience<br />\nfinancierconscience@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n#經濟學ABC<br />\n#經濟學家不等於投資專家<br />\n#要接近市區不如填平維港<br />\n<br />\nwww.thestand.news/society/明日大嶼-願景-成本效益的上佳選擇/<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1031058750272709/posts/2176940142351225/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1031058750272709%2Fposts%2F2176940142351225%2F&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43AEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=6681ef9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1031058750272709/posts/2176940142351225/</a>"},{"pid":"4c740d204b8ff000a631b3b31e7e95e7deaebf8c","tid":892628,"uid":166746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"竟然冇含大"},{"pid":"d5ae86a0739a1599c980dd9a9aa467e69cb6a0fb","tid":892628,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"想睇佢地英文名串"},{"pid":"20dbe92683c14e84096b3018fe5428d89cc1ab89","tid":892628,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ae86a0739a1599c980dd9a9aa467e69cb6a0fb","tid":892628,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"想睇佢地英文名串"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"想睇佢地英文名點串"},{"pid":"b44a0b0ee4d6bc0865c428ff14d54c7533d3688c","tid":892628,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"講真 我個人立場唔介意佢地做<br />\n<br />\n但有兩點我係關注既 <br />\n第一 起完個島質素點？ 一陣就好似沙中線咁 起到成pat屎咁 點樣管理個質素？<br />\n第二 成萬億？ 你玩還玩 你唔好玩到香港收皮呀同你講"},{"pid":"d991d1273aa29e10705ad884c78bf160fce2c62e","tid":892628,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"雷明燈潛咗一排又出來柒"},{"pid":"eea7d2a7b7da49455d19527ce1319c9d28c6797f","tid":892628,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"中大港大多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db79d7e64de54d7bf79ee9cbef354e046e94f287","tid":892628,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"佢計算收入個前題係所謂商業樓面, 有無咁多公司會陪佢地癲搬入去做開荒牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 